4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for beginners aiming to become cybersecurity specialists. Over 16 weeks, students participate in three live online classes weekly with a maximum of 16 participants. The curriculum covers essential skills in Windows, Linux, network, server administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. Additionally, students learn about risk management strategies and international compliance standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, participants receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, recognized by various institutions. Instruction is available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop